outputs.output_descr:
The MDG capacity assessment project seeks to answer the question: "What will it take to achieve the MDGs?" This is not just a question of finance and other resources; it requires strengthened institutional capacity especially to:
•	Strengthen coherence between planning and budget processes
•	Provide a monitoring & accountability framework, and 
•	Support the national policy dialogue & negotiations with development partners
